Package GA_Population

Class Population

java.lang.Object
GA_Population.Population
public class Population extends Object
This is the Population class. This class is solely responsible for maintaing the individuals into ne group. this class contains the following methods: intializePopulation(): used to add the individuals into a population. getFittest(): used to get the fittest of the population. getSecondFittest(): used to get the second fittest of the population. getLeastFittestIndex(): used to get the least fittest of the population so it can be used to be replaced later. calculateFitness(): used to calculate the fitness of the individual.
